- How to verify: so we click in start and make sure the configured correctly , virtual machine 
5. Guest Additions:
    - How to insert Guest Additions:Insert Guest Additions CD image from the menuw bar in the virutal machine it will mount the iso guest assiodions.
- How to run the Guest Additions installer for your Guest Operating System: Open a ubuntu or windowsshall  in the guest operating system.
Navigate to the CD drive where the Guest Additions are mounted.    
- How to change resolution of the VM: need to restart the virtual machine after that we go to view after that virtual screen we choise the reslouion we want .
6. VM Control:
    - Turning on the VM: simply open the vm and and we selct the vm we want to start with ( if we have difffrent one )
    - Turning off the VM: in the guest opration system we choise shut doen or simply right click and shut it down .
